REQUIREMENTS

0) The Gaming Ladder requires a web server with at least PHP version ??? running MySQL version ???.

INSTALLATION

0) Extract the file into the directory you want.

1) Copy 'conf/variables.php.dist' to 'conf/variables.php' and edit the 
settings. Only the database settings are required initially.

2) Extract the file to set up the empty database (located in the conf directory):
gunzip __EmptyDB_rev2__.sql.gz

3) Create the MySQL database
mysql -uusername -p databasename < __EmptyDB_rev2__.sql

4) That's it! Run index.php from the directory you've installed into and all should be working.

5) Go to https://sourceforge.net/projects/gamingladder for more information
